Football at the 2009 Southeast Asian Games
Calcio ai XXV Giochi del Sud-est asiatico

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: Il torneo di calcio ai XXV Giochi del Sud-est asiatico si tenne fra il 2 e il 17 dicembre 2009 a Vientiane.
The football tournament at the 2009 Southeast Asian Games was held in Vientiane, Laos. The men's tournament was played by under-23 national teams, while the women's tournament has no age limit.

Turnamen Sepak bola pada Pesta Olahraga Asia Tenggara 2009 di Vientiane, Laos. Tim nasional yang bermain adalah tim nasional di bawah usia 23 tahun (under 23 years old), sedangkan tim nasional wanita tidak dibatasi usia.
